## 问题描述

当前 agentlog-mcp 的  函数无法识别 OpenClaw Swarm Agent，导致所有 OpenClaw agent 的 session 都显示 source 为 'mcp-tool-call'，无法区分具体是哪个 agent（sentinel、strategist、architect 等）。

## 根因分析

查看 ：

```typescript
function inferSource(clientName: string): string {
  const name = clientName.toLowerCase();

  if (name.includes("opencode")) return "opencode";
  if (name.includes("cline") || name.includes("roo")) return "cline";
  if (name.includes("cursor")) return "cursor";
  if (name.includes("claude")) return "claude-code";
  if (name.includes("copilot") || name.includes("vscode")) return "copilot";
  if (name.includes("continue")) return "continue";
  if (name.includes("trae")) return "trae";

  return "mcp-tool-call";  // <-- OpenClaw agents fall through here
}
```

OpenClaw agent 的 clientInfo.name 通常是 'openclaw' 或类似名称，不匹配任何已知模式。

## 影响

1. 无法在 dashboard 上区分不同 agent 的 session
2. 存证数据丢失 agent 身份信息
3. 统计和分析功能受限

## 修复建议

1. 在 inferSource 中添加 OpenClaw 识别逻辑
2. 或者在 MCP 初始化时通过 metadata 传递 agent 名称
3. 参考 OpenClaw session 的 deliveryContext 来获取正确的 agent 身份

## Bug

`PLUGIN_VERSION` in `packages/openclaw/src/index.ts` reads its own `package.json` via `resolve(dirname(fileURLToPath(import.meta.url)), '..', 'package.json')` — a hard-coded one-level-up assumption.

This should use `packageDirectorySync` from `package-directory` (already available via `@karmaniverous/jeeves`) to reliably find the package root regardless of file layout.

## Current code

```typescript
const dir = dirname(fileURLToPath(import.meta.url));
const pkg = JSON.parse(readFileSync(resolve(dir, '..', 'package.json'), 'utf8'));
```

## Fix

```typescript
import { packageDirectorySync } from 'package-directory';
const pkgRoot = packageDirectorySync({ cwd: fileURLToPath(import.meta.url) });
const pkg = JSON.parse(readFileSync(join(pkgRoot, 'package.json'), 'utf8'));
```

## Related

- karmaniverous/jeeves#57 (same pattern in `createPluginCli`, fixed in core v0.5.0)

